script goal|input|output|how to use
---|---|---|---|---
clean_fasta.sh|converts windows fasta to unix, removes spaces after pipe, removes doubles, removes all non nucleotides|"file".fasta|"file"_cleaned.fasta|bash clean_fasta.sh "file".fasta
cleaner.py|removes segment names from a fasta|"file".fasta|"file"_cleaned.fasta|python cleaner.py "file".fasta
collapse_multifasta.sh|windows to unix, removes spaces after pipe, removes doubles, combines segments in full genome, removes non nucleotides|"file".fasta|"output.fasta"|bash collapse_multifasta.sh "file".fasta "output".fasta
